Upgrade navigation and enhance UI for urban development dashboard
Enhance the UI and functionality of the urban development dashboard.
* **Traffic Prediction (`app/dashboard/predict/page.tsx`)** - Add loading state to the `Button` component. - Display error messages using an `Alert` component. - Improve form validation to ensure all fields are filled before submission.
* **Urban Analysis (`app/dashboard/urban-analysis/page.tsx`)** - Add loading state to the `Button` component. - Display error messages using an `Alert` component. - Add a `Card` component to display analysis results. - Add graphs to visualize analysis results using a chart library.
* **Traffic Flow (`app/dashboard/traffic-flow/page.tsx`)** - Add loading state to the `Button` component. - Display error messages using an `Alert` component. - Improve form validation to ensure all fields are filled before submission. - Add graphs to visualize traffic analysis results using a chart library.
* **Sustainability (`app/dashboard/sustainability/page.tsx`)** - Add loading state to the `Button` component. - Display error messages using an `Alert` component. - Add a `Card` component to display detailed metrics. - Add graphs to visualize sustainability metrics using a chart library.
* **Navigation (`components/navigation.tsx`)** - Upgrade the navigation component to improve user experience and accessibility. - Add new links to the navigation for the new features and pages.
